title: Killer
lyrics:
Baby, how you got no soul?
Is your heart a gaping hole?
How come I didn't see that in you?
How come I can forgive you?
And if you loved me
You wouldn't put me through this

No, If you loved me

You wouldn't put me through it



That makes you a killer, a killer, a killer

That makes you a killer, a killer, a killer



Forever is for dreamers and it's

Foolish to not know you're a schemer

It's silly to think of our unborn children

It's all I'm really thinking about

Right now is just how I will never know them



That makes you a killer, a killer, a killer

That makes you a killer, a killer, a killer
